      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/base/staticdata/asset/common/ListedDerivative
          description: A securitized derivative on another asset.
          deliveryTerm:
            description: |
              Also called contract month or delivery month. However, it's not always a month. It is usually expressed using a code, e.g. Z23 would be the Dec 2023 contract, (Z = December). For crude oil, the corresponding contract might be called CLZ23. Optional as this can be uniquely identified in the identifier.
            type:
              blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
          exchange:
            description: If the Asset is listed, defines the public exchange of the listing.
            type:
              blueId: 6LRw3aCeJHKD7qGzs2HvJDoQiMs8QddUf5wSr4oagtuS
          identifier:
            description: Asset Identifiers are used to uniquely identify an Asset, using a specified Asset Identifier Type.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: B4oXDUH9jELDatvZSw3oWXtJefJ4ixYawEjxBMqSerth
            schema:
              minItems: 1
          instrumentType:
            description: Identifies the type of an instrument using an enumerated list.
            type:
              blueId: EmkPx4XLJeffJqq9EbwZicZCxqAhVBpDz1vu6eP1oTYj
          isExchangeListed:
            description: Defines whether the Asset is listed on a public exchange.
            type:
              blueId: AwvXD961fmnmqcSQhjMA7r15HpVh39cefb6ZTyUz2Fm2
          optionType:
            description: The type of option, ie Put or Call. Left empty if it is a Future.
            type:
              blueId: 4fBHTQQgpt7zfCdmZdM8xKEqaXQv24aeBbn7p8bid744
          relatedExchange:
            description: Provides the related Exchanges, if applicable.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: 6LRw3aCeJHKD7qGzs2HvJDoQiMs8QddUf5wSr4oagtuS
            schema:
              minItems: 0
          strike:
            description: Specifies the strike of the option.
            type:
              blueId: 9eWaHYz2vKrFofdHTHAizNNu8xP6QE3WQ5y7DGrGZvyJ
          taxonomy:
            description: |
              Defines the taxonomy of an object by combining a taxonomy source (i.e. the rules to classify the object) and a value (i.e. the output of those rules on the object.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: 9MYk7MRYjbMWPHe7v3WexZqePowTL8eRrW8TmNNEtzQJ
            schema:
              minItems: 0
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: BRguGmoK69E2QqgFfbDWc1f6YVqxFzv3auepNc48tdFR
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/base/staticdata/asset/common/Loan
          description: Identifies a loan by referencing an asset identifier and through an optional set of attributes.
          borrower:
            description: |
              Specifies the borrower. There can be more than one borrower. It is meant to be used in the event that there is no Bloomberg Id or the Secured List isn't applicable.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: 6LRw3aCeJHKD7qGzs2HvJDoQiMs8QddUf5wSr4oagtuS
            schema:
              minItems: 0
          creditAgreementDate:
            description: |
              Specifies the credit agreement date is the closing date (the date where the agreement has been signed) for the loans in the credit agreement. Funding of the facilities occurs on (or sometimes a little after) the Credit Agreement date. This underlier attribute is used to help identify which of the company's outstanding loans are being referenced by knowing to which credit agreement it belongs. ISDA Standards Terms Supplement term: Date of Original Credit Agreement.
