      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/base/staticdata/asset/credit/NotDomesticCurrency
          description: |
            A class to specify the ISDA 2003 Term: Not Domestic Currency.
          applicable:
            description: Indicates whether the Not Domestic Currency provision is applicable.
            type:
              blueId: AwvXD961fmnmqcSQhjMA7r15HpVh39cefb6ZTyUz2Fm2
            schema:
              required: true
          currency:
            description: |
              An explicit specification of the domestic currency. The list of valid currencies is not presently positioned as an enumeration as part of the CDM because that scope is limited to the values specified by ISDA and FpML. As a result, implementers have to make reference to the relevant standard, such as the ISO 4217 standard for currency codes.
            type:
              blueId: HTDqFgte5VF88dLHnCZMjvyetfxfTAKxf9r8ciErE7Vg
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: GMpNRbtpXncDuLhyddMFw2W43rpm8H6AVYkoczBix3tG
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/base/staticdata/asset/credit/ObligationCategoryEnum
          description: |
            The enumerated values used in both the obligations and deliverable obligations of the credit default swap to represent a class or type of securities which apply.
          type:
            blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
