          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: BMokXsNGeVbH3hGbewvBy1NG4V2DoVoJ7LRURPqGQ2Hz
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/base/staticdata/party/AncillaryEntity
          description: |
            Holds an identifier for an ancillary entity, either identified directly via its ancillary role or directly as a legal entity.
          ancillaryParty:
            description: |
              Identifies a party via its ancillary role on a transaction (e.g. CCP or DCO through which the trade should be cleared.)
            type:
              blueId: C2Ec7JF7c6QV6kD3Wb7Mtfg9NJ7aemu5KqHaafpZuEvN
          legalEntity:
            type:
              blueId: 6LRw3aCeJHKD7qGzs2HvJDoQiMs8QddUf5wSr4oagtuS
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: 5xa7EuQoL6MHLEkfe2xUYenDRD52BrW1dDcJHWhB4zFP
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/base/staticdata/party/AncillaryParty
          description: |
            Defines an ancillary role enumerated value with an associated party reference. The product is agnostic to the actual parties involved in the transaction, with the party references abstracted away from the product definition and replaced by the AncillaryRoleEnum. The AncillaryRoleEnum can then be positioned in the product and this AncillaryParty type, which is positioned outside of the product definition, allows the AncillaryRoleEnum to be associated with an actual party reference.
          onBehalfOf:
            description: Optionally specifies the counterparty that the ancillary party is acting on behalf of.
            type:
              blueId: 6RRexSdxduLUUJjoAGhNuhXszw24mwyTFrHtwAqU2SDG
          partyReference:
            description: Specifies the party, or parties, associated to the ancillary role.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: Doqu2fdYiHUWbSaMDHL5YoyEeuzbTrSjqbT1ZLqmB1Cr
            schema:
              minItems: 1
          role:
            description: |
              Specifies the AncillaryRoleEnum that is associated to the party reference. An ancillary party is any involved party that is not one of the two principal parties to the transaction.
            type:
              blueId: C2Ec7JF7c6QV6kD3Wb7Mtfg9NJ7aemu5KqHaafpZuEvN
            schema:
              required: true
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: 3FLaoJ8BXZUb3VpFoXQ7ACwUhTaDAZgwztubj17GegH4
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/base/staticdata/party/AncillaryRoleEnum
          description: |
            Defines the enumerated values to specify the ancillary roles to the transaction. The product is agnostic to the actual parties involved in the transaction, with the party references abstracted away from the product definition and replaced by the AncillaryRoleEnum. The AncillaryRoleEnum can then be positioned in the product and the AncillaryParty type, which is positioned outside of the product definition, allows the AncillaryRoleEnum to be associated with an actual party reference.
          type:
            blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
          schema:
            enum:
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: CalculationAgentFallback
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: CalculationAgentIndependent
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: CalculationAgentMandatoryEarlyTermination
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: CalculationAgentOptionalEarlyTermination
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: DisruptionEventsDeterminingParty
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: ExerciseNoticeReceiverPartyCancelableProvision
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: ExerciseNoticeReceiverPartyExtendibleProvision
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: ExerciseNoticeReceiverPartyManual
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: ExerciseNoticeReceiverPartyOptionalEarlyTermination
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: ExtraordinaryDividendsParty
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: PredeterminedClearingOrganizationParty
