      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/event/position/AggregationParameters
          description: |
            Parameters to be used to filter events that are relevant to a given portfolio in order to calculate the state of this portfolio. The attributes correspond to all the possible aggregation criteria that can be used and these criteria can be combined. All the attributes are optional.
          dateTime:
            description: To aggregate as of a particular date
            type:
              blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
            schema:
              required: true
          party:
            description: To aggregate based on a selection of party(ies) / legal entity(ies).
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: Doqu2fdYiHUWbSaMDHL5YoyEeuzbTrSjqbT1ZLqmB1Cr
            schema:
              minItems: 0
          positionStatus:
            description: To aggregate based on position status (EXECUTED, SETTLED etc)
            type:
              blueId: CtjNKoKQ8S3xNPyMY6GXJKQAAfjxpTQmdDgLUNE3iAJM
          product:
            description: To aggregate based on a selection of products.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: 8uQuzNQKBLC5kpFy4UH3BU7PPtpbRZEfLQ2ftrsgLHbm#4
            schema:
              minItems: 0
          productQualifier:
            description: To aggregate based on a selection of product type(s).
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
            schema:
              minItems: 0
          totalPosition:
            description: Specifies whether to calculate total position to given date, or only daily position for the given date.
            type:
              blueId: AwvXD961fmnmqcSQhjMA7r15HpVh39cefb6ZTyUz2Fm2
          tradeReference:
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: C5nADRBcWM2dKjXzJRRmahbypM7x2DUsv7Mxpuc9uPRu
            schema:
              minItems: 0
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: 2AjMswvvUFa65tb2E1fgtkxxgJ7ReLj17xorwjbb8wAb
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/event/position/AvailableInventory
          description: |
            A data type that can be used to describe the inventory of securities that a party holds. The securities are held in the AvailableInventoryRecord, with each item in the array being an individual security and its associated criteria. Criteria can include the quantity available, the rate at which the security is available to borrow at, as well as other details that can affect the decision as to whether a party wants to utilise the securities listed.
          availableInventoryRecord:
            description: |
              An array holding the list of inventory being described. Each element in the inventoryRecord array represents an individual piece of inventory i.e. a security.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: 2V4dGZWz8cuGsz2de8Z56U5MbYQwAFwUMekoMx6KF9MR
            schema:
              minItems: 0
          availableInventoryType:
            description: Defines the purpose of this inventory.
            type:
              blueId: aBFCJu2rgHDvt2e9kS3mCjQEMuVFbBnupxJkHCP32WV
            schema:
              required: true
          messageInformation:
            description: Allows details related to the availability messaging use case to be defined
            type:
              blueId: 98dPVuFQFzp6TPmhAh6zjz4zFp8sdg597uHrfF3ztLkP
          party:
            description: |
              Defines all parties involved for the list of inventory records in this set of inventory. For example, when used to describe securities lending availability, this could hold the sender of the availability, the intended recipient, the beneficial owner(s), the lender (which may differ from the sender as the lender may have the same piece of availability going through multiple agents), an agent or a venue.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: 3skPfLDtYJ59SZAAdcu2JDHySdtCEVu8FzTnUX8D5mfy
            schema:
              minItems: 0
          partyRole:
            description: Defines the role(s) that party(ies) may have in relation to the inventory.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: Hrt2EoYJokASG9J62NMKWt8UZbQN6BwtESp7hVDVQYvm
            schema:
              minItems: 0
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: 8gNG5f8FJbRxhdf2sZeitv3B3z4WF4YQTxzMJL1RU2Mb
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/event/position/AvailableInventoryRecord
          description: |
            An individual piece of available inventory. This represents a single security and its associated criteria. The criteria are used to describe any restrictions on the securities.
          collateral:
            description: |
              The type of collateral can often be required when determining if the piece of availability being described is suitable for a party.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: EE9ddWepUCVpA88PcNq8buPwyuFbJawoqrJwAAwpCjcx
            schema:
              minItems: 0
          expirationDateTime:
            description: There may be a set period/time restriction associated to the security.
            type:
              blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
          identifer:
            description: Unique identifier for this record. This can be used to uniquely identify a specific piece of inventory.
            type:
              blueId: HUSEHXgSpK91Brg3mku9fHTV4D8bnuM9D7uwKV2HynTU
          interestRate:
            description: An optional element which can be used to hold a rate associated to this piece of availability.
            type:
              blueId: GLmQaa2vVZKjaht1sNMcUL55xfAgWQxpj5ENxwvVRvsm
          partyRole:
            description: |
              An individual security may be held by several agents. Including the party role at this level allows us to reference the party holding this specific item.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: Hrt2EoYJokASG9J62NMKWt8UZbQN6BwtESp7hVDVQYvm
            schema:
              minItems: 0
          quantity:
