      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/legaldocumentation/master/MasterAgreementClauseVariant
          description: Sets the details for a specific variant associated to a clause in a Master Agreement
          counterparty:
            description: |
              Optional counterparty role. This can be used where a clause needs to assign a different variant to the different parties on the agreement based upon their role i.e. Party A or Party B.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: 6RRexSdxduLUUJjoAGhNuhXszw24mwyTFrHtwAqU2SDG
            schema:
              minItems: 0
              maxItems: 2
          identifier:
            description: Unique identifier for this variant
            type:
              blueId: FrXtTcZdci7tGHhDi1HXMnBCW5ZREz3QTn3enyNDgvxE
            schema:
              required: true
          otherParty:
            description: |
              Optional party. This can be used where a clause needs to assign different variants to different parties who may or may not be on the agreement.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: H6gWEiw9pVTmNQVvvZzt7KcBJ1Ub6wMyaVh3zbM7qCkM
            schema:
              minItems: 0
          variableSet:
            description: |
              For some variants of some clauses additional details are required to work out what has been elected. This array can be used to define the name and value of these variables. Please refer to the agreement documentation for more details of the variables that are available for any clause.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: 7x2TozKfF6tLZmiLa8mcLTM76BnCwyDrjFPBihcxGx5K#0
            schema:
              minItems: 0
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: 7wLk2adpUVoD6AqqF85TpGzcSum1hoSQ8TeAhfcmdpmH
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/legaldocumentation/master/MasterAgreementSchedule
          description: The set of elections which specify a Master Agreement.
          clause:
            description: |
              Clauses that have had elections made against them in this Master Agreement. There must be at least one clause defined in the agreement.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
