      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/observable/asset/MultipleDebtTypes
          description: Represents a class to specify multiple credit debt types alongside a conditional 'any' or 'all' qualifier.
          condition:
            description: An enumerated attribute, to qualify whether All or Any debt type applies.
            type:
              blueId: 5AmXPpNccrpoL5H4BBSk9y2QfnizHY6JKgXqaHJTHgvy
            schema:
              required: true
          debtType:
            description: |
              The type of debt, e.g. long term debt, deposit, ... FpML doesn't specific a scheme value, hence no enumeration is specified as part of the CDM. At least two debt types much be specified.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: HTDqFgte5VF88dLHnCZMjvyetfxfTAKxf9r8ciErE7Vg
