      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/asset/DividendPaymentDate
          description: |
            A class describing the date on which the dividend will be paid/received. This class is also used to specify the date on which the FX rate will be determined, when applicable.
          dividendDate:
            type:
              blueId: EEy3XcQkPgCWJbBTZ5xCt324t2pFRJU6q9odJm19McMd
          dividendDateReference:
            type:
              blueId: 27h9XhtCRRX1w8W56vcSY2T14PTbGigcrhbRWGDy7fKe
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: 555tJWt9LFti4PXtFTEEG8bsobDUDp2ySsgK7sB5kZZ7
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/asset/DividendPayoutRatio
          description: |
            A class describing the dividend payout ratio associated with an equity underlier. In certain cases the actual ratio is not known on trade inception, and only general conditions are then specified.
          basketConstituent:
            description: |
              In the case of a basket underlier, specifies to which component of the basket this particular set of dividend payout ratios correspond.
            type:
              blueId: 9TCszX7p3useiqzNm9UPp1AMdorfkHLknXYXqEVsE2N8
          cashRatio:
            description: |
              Specifies the cash actual dividend payout ratio associated with the equity underlier. A ratio of 90% should be expressed at 0.90.
            type:
              blueId: 9eWaHYz2vKrFofdHTHAizNNu8xP6QE3WQ5y7DGrGZvyJ
          nonCashRatio:
            description: |
              Specifies the non cash actual dividend payout ratio associated with the equity underlier. A ratio of 90% should be expressed at 0.90.
            type:
              blueId: 9eWaHYz2vKrFofdHTHAizNNu8xP6QE3WQ5y7DGrGZvyJ
          totalRatio:
            description: |
              Specifies the total actual dividend payout ratio associated with the equity underlier. A ratio of 90% should be expressed at 0.90.
            type:
              blueId: 9eWaHYz2vKrFofdHTHAizNNu8xP6QE3WQ5y7DGrGZvyJ
            schema:
              required: true
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: CXNX5xUoDwJxfTwLJdwkuXkNThirm3BpXK2QCH6kBkeu
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/asset/DividendPeriod
          description: Time bounded dividend payment periods, each with a dividend payment date per period.
          basketConstituent:
            description: For basket underliers, reference to the basket component which is paying dividends in the specified period.
            type:
              blueId: 9TCszX7p3useiqzNm9UPp1AMdorfkHLknXYXqEVsE2N8
          dateAdjustments:
            description: Date adjustments for all unadjusted dates in this dividend period.
            type:
              blueId: 8ZhZC2EwhTqHnDvvcr2ZW4iwCBJM57NcLAqPCd8shypq
            schema:
              required: true
          dividendPaymentDate:
            description: |
              Specifies when the dividend will be paid to the receiver of the equity return. Has the meaning as defined in the ISDA 2002 Equity Derivatives Definitions. Is not applicable in the case of a dividend reinvestment election.
            type:
              blueId: 555tJWt9LFti4PXtFTEEG8bsobDUDp2ySsgK7sB5kZZ7
            schema:
              required: true
          dividendValuationDate:
            description: Specifies the dividend valuation dates of the swap.
            type:
              blueId: 2Dr79mc7tDo84pCgLDhmSAuay1naC42UUovCTcaMjY5R
          endDate:
            description: Dividend period end date.
            type:
              blueId: 555tJWt9LFti4PXtFTEEG8bsobDUDp2ySsgK7sB5kZZ7
          startDate:
            description: Dividend period start date.
            type:
              blueId: 555tJWt9LFti4PXtFTEEG8bsobDUDp2ySsgK7sB5kZZ7
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: EQ1DnA2mvWsTZJUqo9NJBj9AF7uJYZXPRwQw2ZUqpqQC
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/asset/DividendPeriodEnum
          description: |
            2002 ISDA Equity Derivatives Definitions: First Period, Second Period |
          type:
            blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
          schema:
            enum:
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: FirstPeriod
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: SecondPeriod
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: 4Dvzid1TBuLFxwiAp8Wd2pdhRLvMpCoGBe9D6fba8eVg
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/asset/DividendReturnTerms
          description: |
            A class describing the conditions governing the payment of dividends to the receiver of the equity return, with the exception of the dividend payout ratio, which is defined for each of the underlying components.
          dividendAmountType:
            description: Specifies whether the dividend is paid with respect to the Dividend Period.
            type:
              blueId: EPZXT4tSSu6F1Bgi8FKpq43oaSVqFr8Um1HXaoK25VVE
          dividendComposition:
            description: Specifies how the composition of Dividends is to be determined.
            type:
              blueId: HN4sqTAXi2pGFVHbV6MLLdW3RgQ9Qq4thhJ9rWVsexks
          dividendCurrency:
            description: |
              Specifies the currency in which the dividend will be denominated, e.g. the dividend currency, or a specified currency. This class is not specified as such in FpML, which makes use of the CurrencyAndDeterminationMethod.model to specify such terms.
            type:
              blueId: 6YjggFTd8yUypLgjeUwSiJGZvfraozN2PjZBK4Q8KLQ6
          dividendEntitlement:
            description: Defines the date on which the receiver of the equity return is entitled to the dividend.
            type:
              blueId: 5A3hCLVC8huTr312Z9ddi2snvyWozZsHadHLetvYe31g
          dividendPayoutRatio:
            description: |
              Specifies the dividend payout ratio associated with each underlier. In FpML 5.10 the payout is positioned at the underlier level, although there is an intent to reconsider this approach and position it at the leg level. This is approach adopted by the CDM.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: CXNX5xUoDwJxfTwLJdwkuXkNThirm3BpXK2QCH6kBkeu
            schema:
              minItems: 0
          dividendPeriod:
            description: One to many time bounded dividend payment periods, each with a dividend payment date per period.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: EQ1DnA2mvWsTZJUqo9NJBj9AF7uJYZXPRwQw2ZUqpqQC
            schema:
              minItems: 0
          dividendReinvestment:
            description: Boolean element that defines whether the dividend will be reinvested or not.
            type:
              blueId: AwvXD961fmnmqcSQhjMA7r15HpVh39cefb6ZTyUz2Fm2
          excessDividendAmount:
            description: Determination of Gross Cash Dividend per Share.
            type:
              blueId: EPZXT4tSSu6F1Bgi8FKpq43oaSVqFr8Um1HXaoK25VVE
          extraordinaryDividendsParty:
            description: Specifies the party which determines if dividends are extraordinary in relation to normal levels.
            type:
              blueId: C2Ec7JF7c6QV6kD3Wb7Mtfg9NJ7aemu5KqHaafpZuEvN
          firstOrSecondPeriod:
            description: |
              2002 ISDA Equity Derivatives Definitions: Dividend Period as either the First Period or the Second Period. |
            type:
              blueId: 4Dvzid1TBuLFxwiAp8Wd2pdhRLvMpCoGBe9D6fba8eVg
          materialDividend:
            description: If present and true, then material non cash dividends are applicable.
            type:
              blueId: AwvXD961fmnmqcSQhjMA7r15HpVh39cefb6ZTyUz2Fm2
          nonCashDividendTreatment:
            description: Specifies the treatment of Non-Cash Dividends.
            type:
              blueId: 7X5DcG9JMYrcW7XQWvsmFc2zX3uk1rsikycU2gBnKSyV
          performance:
            description: |
              Performance calculation, in accordance with Part 1 Section 12 of the 2018 ISDA CDM Equity Confirmation for Security Equity Swap, Para 75. 'Equity Performance'. Cumulative performance is used as a notional multiplier factor on both legs of an Equity Swap.
            type:
              blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
          specialDividends:
            description: Specifies the method according to which special dividends are determined.
            type:
              blueId: AwvXD961fmnmqcSQhjMA7r15HpVh39cefb6ZTyUz2Fm2
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: J8EZbmYAMd5iEdiJDjh3B8Pk6R4eAXrQdryNuThytk1B
            attributesAdded: []
