          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: 7X5DcG9JMYrcW7XQWvsmFc2zX3uk1rsikycU2gBnKSyV
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/asset/PriceReturnTerms
          conversionFactor:
            description: |
              Defines the conversion applied if the quantity unit on contract is different from unit on referenced underlier.
            type:
              blueId: 9eWaHYz2vKrFofdHTHAizNNu8xP6QE3WQ5y7DGrGZvyJ
          performance:
            description: |
              Performance calculation, in accordance with Part 1 Section 12 of the 2018 ISDA CDM Equity Confirmation for Security Equity Swap, Para 75. 'Equity Performance'. Cumulative performance is used as a notional multiplier factor on both legs of an Equity Swap.
            type:
              blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
          returnType:
            description: The type of return associated with the equity swap.
            type:
              blueId: EvqKp8C4TsU58D4ZoFC8ba55Fdq8Qeka9NmEAAuioCk3
            schema:
              required: true
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: JAFJ1wyCKHfmK69wvo8tXGepwZYTJ4o37xsdPgsDstzv
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/asset/ProtectionTerms
          description: |
            A class to specify the terms for calculating a payout to protect the buyer of the swap in the case of a qualified credit event. These terms include the applicable credit events, the reference obligation, and in the case of a CDS on mortgage-backed securities, the floatingAmountEvents.
          creditEvents:
            description: |
              Specifies the applicable Credit Events that would trigger a settlement, as specified in the related Confirmation and defined in the ISDA 2014 Credit Definition article IV section 4.1.
            type:
              blueId: 3VWXt9VeCTwLSaTRa6KebXPdyz4Gy3Xwf33wBbvgbeqo
          floatingAmountEvents:
            description: |
              This element contains the ISDA terms relating to the floating rate payment events and the implied additional fixed payments, applicable to the credit derivatives transactions on mortgage-backed securities with pay-as-you-go or physical settlement.
            type:
              blueId: 5arWKUo6ZdrsnkGXoVp8CVH4YWcUpQsCZ1EdqkBn5py5
          obligations:
            description: |
              The underlying obligations of the reference entity on which you are buying or selling protection. The credit events Failure to Pay, Obligation Acceleration, Obligation Default, Restructuring, Repudiation/Moratorium are defined with respect to these obligations.
            type:
              blueId: 8hht48mGH2ZK8VFHr71MXDR5Mrge37JSMeCJn1DTKdxt
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: 6p917qiqhcPsLDv4c6fcokZDb38SkP1i69kThgdzHgBY
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/asset/RateSpecification
          description: A data type to specify the fixed interest rate, floating interest rate or inflation rate.
          FixedRateSpecification:
            description: The fixed rate or fixed rate specification expressed as explicit fixed rates and dates.
            type:
              blueId: 9svusKr6LvCBhk7gV6JsbPAwwXWASiSTahN4JPrDC5rH
          FloatingRateSpecification:
            description: |
              The floating interest rate specification, which includes the definition of the floating rate index. the tenor, the initial value, and, when applicable, the spread, the rounding convention, the averaging method and the negative interest rate treatment.
            type:
              blueId: 7Qg4XRChRagWG1WXXQ6SxKQFUAWi38ZztLZRLJigyUr8
          InflationRateSpecification:
            description: An inflation rate calculation definition.
            type:
              blueId: FWV3Br4aKDWruqfn5vhLVt6xEv37srRU5k5YncDQvGnz
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: 6sGfKpzEcNGWsWw9v54bkUTJDbBHqbhEeJFCsf6tUhXf
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/asset/RateTreatmentEnum
          description: The enumerated values to specify the methods for converting rates from one basis to another.
          type:
            blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
          schema:
            enum:
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: BondEquivalentYield
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
                value: MoneyMarketYield
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: 6vYpwpDGdaR6pbtzmJTTxmLwiWsbwBhhaiecmRbLMtix
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/asset/RealisedVarianceMethodEnum
          description: |
            The contract specifies which price must satisfy the boundary condition.  Used for variance, volatility and correlation caps and floors.
          type:
            blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
          schema:
            enum:
              - type:
                  blueId: GX7CFUmSDrE2MzptunLCCdZwnuwwrenRQqEnHL4x3uoC
