      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/collateral/Collateral
          description: A type for defining the obligations of the counterparty subject to credit support requirements.
          collateralPortfolio:
            description: |
              The collateral portfolios which contain the collateral which covers a trade. (NB: this can be provided by reference to a global key for each CollateralPortfolio object)
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: 4BrXNc4oFsUfnFzm3uWTqNmgivGhZJRmaoxvb8kK9xiw
            schema:
              minItems: 0
          collateralProvisions:
            description: specifies the collateral provisions of the product.
            type:
              blueId: EE9ddWepUCVpA88PcNq8buPwyuFbJawoqrJwAAwpCjcx
          independentAmount:
            description: |
              Independent Amount is an amount that usually less creditworthy counterparties are asked to provide. It can either be a fixed amount or a percentage of the Transaction's value. The Independent Amount can be: (i) transferred before any trading between the parties occurs (as a deposit at a third party's account or with the counterparty) or (ii) callable after trading has occurred (typically because a downgrade has occurred). In situation (i), the Independent Amount is not included in the calculation of Exposure, but in situation (ii), it is included in the calculation of Exposure. Thus, for situation (ii), the Independent Amount may be transferred along with any collateral call. Independent Amount is a defined term in the ISDA Credit Support Annex. ('with respect to a party, the amount specified as such for that party in Paragraph 13; if no amount is specified, zero').
            type:
              blueId: Bx6RbJH85Gh7BbnBoSUaTvzqwCNheMpjmwzdouE6UJz
          portfolioIdentifier:
            description: A list of identifiers pointing to the collateral portfolios which contain the collateral which covers a trade.
            type:
              blueId: 8DSFoWG9MqRSUhStqoPLrwVQiYByRh18NWbDEarN8MKF
            itemType:
              blueId: 9tpFoqFu1yX5LZEATGF8CYsE5VSXhkQua9LMXwLEX2Pv
            schema:
              minItems: 0
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: 6jhHzxNcd11YEG9a9f1yBWhmm5qpzmbZ6E7JEqHpPj7r
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/collateral/CollateralAgreementFloatingRate
          description: Represents the parameters needed to calculate the floating rate paid on collateral holdings.
          capRateSchedule:
            description: |
              The cap rate or cap rate schedule, if any, which applies to the floating rate. The cap rate (strike) is only required where the floating rate on a swap stream is capped at a certain level. A cap rate schedule is expressed as explicit cap rates and dates and the step dates may be subject to adjustment in accordance with any adjustments specified in calculationPeriodDatesAdjustments. The cap rate is assumed to be exclusive of any spread and is a per annum rate, expressed as a decimal. A cap rate of 5% would be represented as 0.05.
            type:
              blueId: 6YLNUc4mUyAXJnpaEm2W4KAfb1HUCDcrXqv7KetjrbwH
          compressibleSpread:
            description: |
              Specifies how spreads should be applied in a low/negative rate environment.  If true, spread is applied only if rate is positive.
            type:
              blueId: AwvXD961fmnmqcSQhjMA7r15HpVh39cefb6ZTyUz2Fm2
            schema:
              required: true
          floorRateSchedule:
            description: |
              The floor rate or floor rate schedule, if any, which applies to the floating rate. The floor rate (strike) is only required where the floating rate on a swap stream is floored at a certain strike level. A floor rate schedule is expressed as explicit floor rates and dates and the step dates may be subject to adjustment in accordance with any adjustments specified in calculationPeriodDatesAdjustments. The floor rate is assumed to be exclusive of any spread and is a per annum rate, expressed as a decimal. A floor rate of 5% would be represented as 0.05.
            type:
              blueId: 6YLNUc4mUyAXJnpaEm2W4KAfb1HUCDcrXqv7KetjrbwH
          negativeInterest:
            description: |
              Specifies how negative rates should be applied.  If rates go negative, should the payment be reversed (true) or zeroed out (false)?
            type:
              blueId: AwvXD961fmnmqcSQhjMA7r15HpVh39cefb6ZTyUz2Fm2
            schema:
              required: true
          rateOption:
            type:
              blueId: 4G54JBxkdxEwLZwmqaWCK5bKJB6A4GG18uBgBUKxJ4am
          spreadSchedule:
            description: |
              The ISDA Spread or a Spread schedule expressed as explicit spreads and dates. In the case of a schedule, the step dates may be subject to adjustment in accordance with any adjustments specified in calculationPeriodDatesAdjustments. The spread is a per annum rate, expressed as a decimal. For purposes of determining a calculation period amount, if positive the spread will be added to the floating rate and if negative the spread will be subtracted from the floating rate. A positive 10 basis point (0.1%) spread would be represented as 0.001.
            type:
              blueId: BbmQzuzA7aBEkeWMx9NniHvZEqR3bPsBJzX8iyyokN7A
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: 9je4gdfYWh5s9PxZCf36xymmiBGd59PHPrBapq7pnGVf
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
          name: cdm/product/collateral/CollateralCriteria
          description: |
            The possible different terms that can be combined, using AND, OR and NOT logic, to define the issuers and/or assets that meet a given criteria for collateral.
          AllCriteria:
            description: Enables two or more Collateral Criteria to be combined using AND logic.
            type:
              blueId: this#2
          AnyCriteria:
            description: Enables two or more Collateral Criteria to be combined using OR logic.
            type:
              blueId: this#0
          AssetAgencyRating:
            description: Criteria is the agency rating(s) of the collateral asset.
            type:
              blueId: 4wRJXUzN8uTkKFeHycmg5s4LPtKSpfJSj9cRXHx5JAsi
          AssetCountryOfOrigin:
            description: Criteria is the collateral asset country of origin.
            type:
              blueId: FCuNiKfbXacwA5Cb4PtQoxUqheV4siYC6kq5GkcmGBvM
          AssetMaturity:
            description: Criteria is the maturity characteristics of the collateral asset.
            type:
              blueId: DvHC67ebizujZAhviEeMQ82ZhicijkGL6dTdyk24smo3
          AssetType:
            description: Criteria is the asset type of the collateral.
            type:
              blueId: AjHv57wVryq4YK8oodLNAT95JAYhuGRRiKk7hhX93LLi
          CollateralIssuerType:
            description: Criteria is the type of entity issuing the asset.
            type:
              blueId: GL9FygufGouoWPdbzaZ4SKyuRahWMAUxZ5q3bFMSWnRj
          CollateralTaxonomy:
            description: Criteria is the taxonomy characteristics of an collateral.
            type:
              blueId: 6FkJxLK4KiPuQ7LHqQDvpGSeaWMVr5dw4g2K9mBrnybJ
          CounterpartyOwnIssuePermitted:
            description: Criteria includes collateral issued by the counterparty.
            type:
              blueId: BSxC7wcq6PvdbEFuVkkBrzKz4bFBiG8He3PZk9SqFFeQ
          CurrencyCodeEnum:
            description: Criteria is the denominated currency of the collateral.
            type:
              blueId: Gb5ryH6JKgjNLySafKo7tXkb9PRgaQkWHcSibFZ96AbP
          DomesticCurrencyIssued:
            description: Criteria is that collateral must be denominated in the domestic currency of the issuer.
            type:
              blueId: GSqFLxJkjPptdZcwACBFg4PMYhDwpuNcRBdKtNHgs4Wn
          Index:
            description: Criteria is that the collateral is a constituent of a specific index.
            type:
              blueId: FtoRYZujAAg27pRyk4p13wRUXC9JWtWMkcjiAZULxMWP
          IssuerAgencyRating:
            description: Criteria is the agency rating(s) of the issuer.
            type:
              blueId: BQF5ff4etcuh9njP6VFEZiHKExrKnVkMbMrfqE7wkWHq
          IssuerCountryOfOrigin:
            description: Criteria is the issuing entity country of origin.
            type:
              blueId: 9qB83hxGqypCsEF6MKyZFWjg9t2VMnqgDMywCd2LCh6z
          IssuerName:
            description: Criteria is a specific named issuer entity.
            type:
              blueId: 9bkUNZgKaw1Cro32d1MxEwS5ZxRXwMi6iFvMNGxgekBC
          ListingExchange:
            description: Criteria is that the collateral is listed on a specific exchange.
            type:
              blueId: BzgPMJPnH7Cq2NK4PkNTKXVrpY3u3BUxB9jjvKLAxpq8
          ListingSector:
            description: Criteria is the industry sector of the collateral asset.
            type:
              blueId: 2sRSP8xV5oTb6nySDWzH4ZcHxhHkKtMgqw73G2Y7kwC8
          NegativeCriteria:
            description: Enables a single Collateral Criteria to be excluded using NOT logic.
            type:
              blueId: this#3
          SovereignAgencyRating:
            description: Criteria is the agency rating(s) of the country of the issuer.
            type:
              blueId: 8tRrLY27bAdfQuvV7dnmS5iQ1QW6VFmjUB7KsaAjNpQv
          SpecificAsset:
            description: Criteria is a specifically identified asset
            type:
              blueId: 2Gr3Akes7mjaFvgw48PJ56oasjq7iSukKYHpJJZcCwCS
        versions:
          - repositoryVersionIndex: 0
            typeBlueId: HGtVL5zUGD9Z8S6VLuBSEyhaVDP2h8eWzt5te5sS8iTo#1
            attributesAdded: []
      - status: stable
        content:
